     <td class="usermenu"> <em><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="fontSize('m','textstyle_59')" title="减小帖子内容字体">小</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="fontSize('b','textstyle_59')" title="增大帖子内容字体">大</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;59楼</em> <a href="userspace.asp?sid=45465">个性首页</a> | <a href="tencent://message/?uin=1299070147" title="点击发送QQ消息给zzy">QQ</a> | <a href="dispuser.asp?id=45465" target="_blank" title="查看zzy的个人资料">信息</a> | <a href="query.asp?stype=1&amp;nSearch=3&amp;keyword=zzy&amp;BoardID=21&amp;SearchDate=ALL" target="_blank" title="搜索zzy在保险投诉的所有帖子">搜索</a> | <a href="mailto:0ZZY@163.com" title="点击这里发送电子邮件给zzy">邮箱</a> | <a href="http://阿远哥哥（博客：分设在和讯网、新浪网）" target="_blank" title="访问zzy的主页">主页</a> | <a href="http://service.51uc.com/user_info/show_user_info_base.shtml?UID=" title="zzy的UC情况" target="_blank">UC</a> </td> 
